# 🚗 Drive By Rihem - Car Rental Website

## 📖 Description

Drive By Rihem is a modern and responsive car rental website designed for a Tunisian car rental company.

The goal of this project is to provide users with an attractive and user-friendly platform where they can:

- Discover available rental vehicles
- Check current promotions
- Make reservations
- Learn more about the company
- Contact the agency

This project was developed using only HTML5 and CSS3.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🏠 Home Page
- Responsive navigation bar
- Company logo
- User action icons

### 🎁 Promotions Section
- Promotional offers
- Featured vehicles
- Booking buttons

### 📅 Reservation Section
- Pick-up location
- Pick-up date and time
- Drop-off date and time
- Reservation request button

### 🚘 Vehicle Catalog
- Featured cars
- Daily pricing
- Quote and booking options

### ⭐ Services
- Professional service information
- Agency locations

### ℹ️ About Us
- Company presentation
- Agency image
- Booking call-to-action

### 🔒 Why Choose Us
- Safe & Insured
- 24/7 Support
- Best Prices

### 📞 Footer
- Airport agencies
- City agencies
- Useful links
- Payment methods
- Social media links

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Font Awesome
- Google Fonts

