## 🚀 Getting Started

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/drive-by-rihem.git
```

2. Open the project folder

```bash
cd drive-by-rihem
```

3. Open `index.html` in your browser

No additional installation is required.

---

## 📱 Responsive Design

The website is fully responsive and optimized for:

- Desktop
- Laptop
- Tablet
- Mobile Devices

CSS Flexbox, Grid, and Media Queries are used to ensure a smooth experience across all screen sizes.

